PREP TRACK AND FIELD ROUNDUP; YANKOFF BOOSTS SANTA MARGARITA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Derek Yankoff, who was Santa Margarita's quarterback and a guard on the 
basketball team, competed in his first high school track meet and helped the 
Eagles to an 87-47 victory over University in a Sea View League meet Thursday 
at Santa Margarita. 
</P>
<P>
 Yankoff won the long jump (20 feet 2 inches) and the triple jump (40-8). 
Teammate Josh Budimlya won the both hurdle races, the 100 in 16.5 second and 
the 300 in 43.5. 
