<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY: WASTE DISPOSAL CONTRACT WON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Security Environmental Systems Inc. said Wednesday that it has won a $500,000 
hazardous waste disposal contract from a leading aerospace company in Southern 
California. 
</P>
<P>
 Security Environmental officials said the aerospace company did not grant 
permission for its identity to be revealed. The one-year account is the first 
that Security Environmental has won from a major aerospace client. 
</P>
