<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Nona Morelli's II Casino Deal: Cleopatra Palace Ltd. of Ireland said it has 
received permission to run a casino in the North African country of Tunisia 
with Irvine-based Nona Morelli's II. 
</P>
<P>
 Nona Morelli's put up $6 million in working capital in exchange for 70% of 
Cleopatra. The casino is set to open in 1995; construction of a hotel and 250 
condominiums has already begun. 
</P>
<P>
 Nona Morelli's II invests in casinos and makes pasta and sauces. 
</P>
