<P>
Sidebar 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032594-0288 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 026276 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 25, 1994, Friday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 24; Column 3; Metro Desk 
